Go back to [[Help:Widgets | Widgets ]]
==== Configuration Settings ====

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.widget.CalloutWidget
}}

==== Example ====

The widget can be embedded in the wiki page with the following code:
<source>
{{#widget: Callout | 
 title = 'Click Me...'
 | callout = 
   {{ text = '<b>Hi</b> there!'
    | title = 'Hi'
   }}
 | width = '100'
 | image = '/images/iwb_logo_margin.png'
}}
</source>

The resulted view :

{{#widget: Callout | 
 title = 'Click Me...'
 | callout = 
   {{ text = '<b>Hi</b> there!'
    | title = 'Hi'
   }}
 | width = '100'
 | image = '/images/iwb_logo_margin.png'
}}